name: E.T.: The Extra-Terrestrial - The Green Planet
name_original: E.T.: The Extra-Terrestrial - The Green Planet
description:
E.T.: The Extra-Terrestrial - The Green Planet is a strategy game developed by Strawdog Studios. It was originally released in 2012. It was published by Chillingo.
E.T.: The Extra-Terrestrial - The Green Planet is available on iOS.
